msgstr ""

#: data/campaigns/Liberty/scenarios/01_The_Raid.cfg:137 data/campaigns/Liberty/scenarios/01_The_Raid.cfg:142 data/campaigns/Liberty/scenarios/01_The_Raid.cfg:147
